name: VeeCon 2022 #239
description:
VeeCon 2022 - Created By Snowfro and Gary Vaynerchuk.

This token is a verifiable ticket for admission to VeeCon 2022, which is a multi-day event exclusively created for VeeFriends & the Web3 community.

Time: May 19th - May 22nd, 2022

Location: U.S. Bank Stadium in Minneapolis, MN, USA

To be admitted to VeeCon 2022, attendees must hold this token in a mobile-compatible NFT wallet and register it for admission with the official VeeCon event app. The VeeCon event and ticket registration app will be released in May 2022 on iOS and Android and will be used for verifiable ownership of this NFT, event registration, and programming.

To commemorate the first ever VeeCon conference, VeeFriends is honored to collaborate with Web 3 pioneer Erick 'Snowfro' Calderon. Snowfro, the founder of Art Blocks, a first of its kind generative blockchain platform, and creator of the Chromie Squiggle, collaborated on this collection during early Spring 2022 with Gary Vaynerchuk, the creator and visionary behind VeeFriends. Snowfro's squiqqles and Gary's doodles have melded together to create the artwork for the first NFT ticketed conference and to live forever on the ethereum blockchain.

If you plan to attend VeeCon 2022 with this ticket NFT please RSVP now at [VeeCon.co/RSVP](https://veecon.co/rsvp)

Instructions for how to use this ticket to gain admission to VeeCon are coming soon to [VeeCon.co](https://veecon.co/)!
